description: Details pursuant to outline consent granted 19/08/99 for redevelopment of former Kingsbury Hospital site for healthcare facility and residential development.  Details relate only to residential development and to condition 4 reserved matters (siting, design and external appearance), condition 5 (street layout, internal layout, boundary treatment, fenestration, etc.) for the erection of a total of 121 dwellings comprising 83 dwellings for private market (14 no. 3-bed houses, 24 no. 4-bed houses, 37 no. 2-bed flats and 8 no. 1-bed flats) and 38 dwellings for affordable housing purposes (26 no. 3-bed houses, 4 no. 4-bed houses and 8 no. 2-bed flats)
